{
  "video_id": "oNNZO9i1Gjc",
  "title": "Holy Spirit",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1000.0,
      "end_time": 4200.0,
      "text": "If you have ever heard the phrase \"the Holy Spirit\""
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4200.0,
      "end_time": 5180.0,
      "text": "and you want to know what it means,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5180.0,
      "end_time": 6100.0,
      "text": "where do you start?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6100.0,
      "end_time": 8840.0,
      "text": "Well, you have to start on page one of the Bible."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8840.0,
      "end_time": 11520.0,
      "text": "Where the uncreated world is depicted as this"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11520.0,
      "end_time": 13740.0,
      "text": "dark chaotic place. But then, above the chaos"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 13740.0,
      "end_time": 18440.0,
      "text": "God's Spirit is there, hovering, ready to bring about life and order and beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 18440.0,
      "end_time": 20700.0,
      "text": "Okay, but what is God's Spirit?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 20700.0,
      "end_time": 23980.0,
      "text": "Yeah, so the Spirit is the way the Biblical authors"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 23980.0,
      "end_time": 25920.0,
      "text": "talk about God's personal presence."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 25920.0,
      "end_time": 27600.0,
      "text": "The Hebrew word is Ruakh."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 27600.0,
      "end_time": 30540.0,
      "text": "Ruu-a-achh? Yeah, you've gotta clear your throat at the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 30540.0,
      "end_time": 31540.0,
      "text": "So, what is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 31540.0,
      "end_time": 34100.0,
      "text": "Ruakh can refer to a number of different things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 34100.0,
      "end_time": 36780.0,
      "text": "but what they all have in common is energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 36780.0,
      "end_time": 38100.0,
      "text": "Energy? How so?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 38100.0,
      "end_time": 40100.0,
      "text": "So, there's an invisible energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 40100.0,
      "end_time": 42420.0,
      "text": "that makes the clouds move or the tree branches sway."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 42420.0,
      "end_time": 44640.0,
      "text": "Right, wind. So in Hebrew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 44640.0,
      "end_time": 46800.0,
      "text": "that's Ruakh. Okay!"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 46800.0,
      "end_time": 48340.0,
      "text": "Now, take a big breath, uwwshh!"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 48340.0,
      "end_time": 49740.0,
      "text": "So you feel that, inside you."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 49740.0,
      "end_time": 50860.0,
      "text": "Yeah, the air?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 50860.0,
      "end_time": 52860.0,
      "text": "Well, specifically the energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 52860.0,
      "end_time": 54860.0,
      "text": "right, the vitality in your body that you get from"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 54860.0,
      "end_time": 56540.0,
      "text": "breathing, deeply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 56540.0,
      "end_time": 58540.0,
      "text": "that too is, Ruakh."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 58540.0,
      "end_time": 60540.0,
      "text": "And this is the same word"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 60540.0,
      "end_time": 62540.0,
      "text": "used in the Bible, to describe God's"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 62540.0,
      "end_time": 63840.0,
      "text": "personal presence."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 63840.0,
      "end_time": 65700.0,
      "text": "Just like wind and breath are invisible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 65700.0,
      "end_time": 67780.0,
      "text": "God's spirit, is invisible."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 67780.0,
      "end_time": 71340.0,
      "text": "Wind is powerful, and so God's spirit is powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 71340.0,
      "end_time": 73180.0,
      "text": "And just as breath keeps us alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 73180.0,
      "end_time": 76100.0,
      "text": "so God's spirit sustains all of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 76100.0,
      "end_time": 77700.0,
      "text": "Yeah! Ruakh."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 77700.0,
      "end_time": 78200.0,
      "text": "Now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 78200.0,
      "end_time": 80480.0,
      "text": "as we continue on in the story of the Bible"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 80480.0,
      "end_time": 85300.0,
      "text": "We see God's ruakh giving special empowerment to people for specific tasks."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 85300.0,
      "end_time": 87080.0,
      "text": "The first person in the Bible that happens to"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 87080.0,
      "end_time": 87580.0,
      "text": "is Joseph"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 88080.0,
      "end_time": 91520.0,
      "text": "God's spirit enables him to understand and interpret dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 91520.0,
      "end_time": 94840.0,
      "text": "And then it happens to this guy named \"Betsaleel\" and he's an artist!"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 94840.0,
      "end_time": 97500.0,
      "text": "God's spirit empowers him with wisdom and skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 97500.0,
      "end_time": 101660.0,
      "text": "He's given creative genius to make beautiful things in the tabernacle."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 101660.0,
      "end_time": 106000.0,
      "text": "And we also see God's ruakh empower a group of people called \"the prophets\"."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 106000.0,
      "end_time": 109940.0,
      "text": "They're able to see what's happening  in history from God's point of view."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 109940.0,
      "end_time": 110940.0,
      "text": "That's exactly right!"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 110940.0,
      "end_time": 113820.0,
      "text": "And here's the problem as the prophet saw it."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 113820.0,
      "end_time": 117000.0,
      "text": "While God's ruakh had created a really good world"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 117000.0,
      "end_time": 119100.0,
      "text": "humans have given in to evil."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 119100.0,
      "end_time": 122280.0,
      "text": "They've unleashed chaos into it through their injustice."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 122280.0,
      "end_time": 123860.0,
      "text": "A new type of disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 123860.0,
      "end_time": 124480.0,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 124480.0,
      "end_time": 126680.0,
      "text": "And the prophet said the spirit would come,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 126680.0,
      "end_time": 128260.0,
      "text": "just like in Genesis 1,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 128259.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130599.99999999999,
      "text": "but now, to transform the human heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 130600.0,
      "end_time": 134000.0,
      "text": "to empower people to truly love God and others."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 134000.0,
      "end_time": 136820.0,
      "text": "How will this new active God spirit happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 136820.0,
      "end_time": 140380.0,
      "text": "Well, centuries past and we're introduced to Jesus."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 140380.0,
      "end_time": 141720.0,
      "text": "And at the beginning of his mission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 141720.0,
      "end_time": 146540.0,
      "text": "there's a beautiful scene where Jesus is being baptized in the waters of the Jordan river."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 146540.0,
      "end_time": 151600.0,
      "text": "Yeah, the sky opens up and God's spirit comes and rests on him like a bird."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 151600.0,
      "end_time": 156960.0,
      "text": "The story sang that God's spirit is empowering Jesus to begin the new creation."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 156960.0,
      "end_time": 160740.0,
      "text": "And we see this happening when he heals people or forgives their sins."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 160740.0,
      "end_time": 164180.0,
      "text": "He's creating life where there once was death."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 164180.0,
      "end_time": 168580.0,
      "text": "Now, Israel's religious leaders oppose Jesus and they eventually have him killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 168580.0,
      "end_time": 171520.0,
      "text": "But even here, God's spirit is at work."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 171520.0,
      "end_time": 174960.0,
      "text": "The earliest disciples of Jesus who saw him alive from the dead"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 174960.0,
      "end_time": 179200.0,
      "text": "said it was God's energizing spirit that raised Jesus."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 179200.0,
      "end_time": 181640.0,
      "text": "This is the beginning of new creation."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 181640.0,
      "end_time": 183180.0,
      "text": "Yes, and it is still going."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 183180.0,
      "end_time": 185900.0,
      "text": "When Jesus appeared to his closest followers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 185900.0,
      "end_time": 189560.0,
      "text": "he breathed on them and said \"Receive the Holy Spirit.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 189560.0,
      "end_time": 193420.0,
      "text": "And soon after that, the Spirit powerfully comes on all of his disciples."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 193420.0,
      "end_time": 197080.0,
      "text": "So that they can become a part of this new creation"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 197080.0,
      "end_time": 203040.0,
      "text": "and share the good news and learn how to live by the energy and influence of God's spirit."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 203040.0,
      "end_time": 207460.0,
      "text": "And so today, the spirit is still hovering in dark places."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 207460.0,
      "end_time": 209640.0,
      "text": "Yes, pointing people to Jesus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 209640.0,
      "end_time": 214160.0,
      "text": "transforming and empowering them so they can love God and others."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 214160.0,
      "end_time": 217780.0,
      "text": "And the Christian hope is that the Spirit is going to finish the job."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 217780.0,
      "end_time": 221580.0,
      "text": "The story of the Bible ends with a vision of a new humanity"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 221580.0,
      "end_time": 231580.0,
      "text": "living in a new world that's permeated with God's love and life-giving spirit."
    }
  ]
}